# The relay's hot key (0x-prefixed 32-byte hex). LOW-VALUE by design: it can
# only pay gas to deliver signed votes — it can censor, never forge. Fund it
# with a small native balance on every enabled chain; watch /healthz.
RELAY_PRIVATE_KEY=

# HTTP port (default 8787) and SQLite path (default relay.db, relative to relay/).
# RELAY_PORT=8787
# RELAY_DB_PATH=relay.db

# Per-chain overrides of relay.config.json (chainId-suffixed). A chain whose
# deployer resolves to empty/null is DISABLED (fail closed, loudly logged).
# RELAY_RPC_URL_100=
# RELAY_DEPLOYER_100=
# RELAY_RPC_URL_42161=
# RELAY_DEPLOYER_42161=
# RELAY_RPC_URL_10=
# RELAY_DEPLOYER_10=
# RELAY_RPC_URL_1=
# RELAY_DEPLOYER_1=
